Class NeuronCannotFireException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.riskybusiness.neural.NeuronCannotFireException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NeuronCannotFireException
extends RuntimeException

        A basic Exception that tells us that a Neuron could not fire. This could be due to programmer restrictions, implementation issues, but most likely the fact that the Neuron did not have enough inputs to fire.

    Since:
    1.6
